.*
# Re-include the `.noop_down` marker files used by the migration round-trip
# harness in `src-tauri/tests/migrations.rs`. Without this exception the
# `.*` rule above would silently drop newly added markers from commits and
# defeat the safety net that opts a migration out of the up/down assertion.
!src-tauri/migrations/*/.noop_down
